Charlie Weber (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlie_Weber_(actor) 0 Charles Alan "Charlie" Weber Jr. (born September 20, 1978) is an American actor and former model. In 2014, Weber began starring as Frank Delfino in the ABC legal drama series, How to Get Away with Murder.
